{"tid":1966059,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊潤雄：若確診持續減少文憑試很大機會如期開考","createTime":"2020-04-10T02:04:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T03:11:16.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b42348a9a1e01671273bf7b92287c86e9acaa257","tid":1966059,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"楊潤雄：若確診持續減少文憑試很大機會如期開考<br />\n10.04.2020 09:50<br />\n<br />\n教育局長楊潤雄在本台節目表示，現時仍然以今個月24號開考中學文憑試為目標，留意到近日本港確診個案有減少，指趨勢持續，如期開考的機會很大，唯一考慮是疫情變化，要平衡學生安全及考試需要。他舉例指，若下星期有疫情爆發，而未能阻止病毒擴散，可能要延遲開考。<br />\n<br />\n楊潤雄又說，已經要求提供試場的學校，考試期間開放校內所有洗手間，縮減考生排隊去廁所的時間。他又預料整個考試期內，學校復課的機會都很微，近兩星期局方有與大學討論，若文憑試未能順利舉行，可能要為學生另作評估。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279923&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279923%26csid%3D261_341&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi65rbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=8d6e764e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279923&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2ca7e2b7475d5d0ed260e1ac0d0bfd1945abdd74","tid":1966059,"uid":352564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"推一班莘莘學子去刑場"},{"pid":"dd74c5a42f168341ae345b223537bdaddfdc0195","tid":1966059,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ca7e2b7475d5d0ed260e1ac0d0bfd1945abdd74","tid":1966059,"uid":352564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"推一班莘莘學子去刑場"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:11:41.000Z","msg":"其實唔考對考生都係精神折磨多一年<br />\n<br />\n考好過唔考"},{"pid":"ff5c019fc775b03abdab01a6cb2171e7c04e58da","tid":1966059,"uid":355064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"點都一尻樣"},{"pid":"dae31cf72bbd09a4be1194ff87145b5d55ceb676","tid":1966059,"uid":12877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ca7e2b7475d5d0ed260e